    "description": "Are you a skilled Digital Marketing Manager looking for your next big career move? Zepto South Asia Partners in Varanasi offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Zepto South Asia Partners:\nZepto South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Magento\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zepto South Asia Partners!",
